item.title: CVE-2012-6114|2024-08-06T21:28:39.424Z -- git-extras -- git-extras
item.description: The git-changelog utility in git-extras 1.7.0 allows local users to overwrite arbitrary files via a symlink attack on (1) /tmp/changelog or (2) /tmp/.git-effort.
